{
  "stem": "1603.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] then we didn't see her, but we were listening to a British radio, Hungarian broadcasting, which was against the law.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's how we learned that Hannah made it to England but volunteered with the British to come back, fly back, over Hungary and be parachuted in the Hungarian territory and be a spy [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for the allies, which she did.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she got captured.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When she parachuted out, they spotted her, and they captured her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I know the prison where she was kept exactly, because I went there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I went back to Hungary, I put my hand on the walls where she was just to touch it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we have-- on the Buda side, we have a place, a little tunnel which goes-- goes through a small mountain.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when you go-- before you go into that little tunnel, to the right-hand side there was a prison there where she-- she was kept.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very close to the Danube River.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so she was kept there and never for one second she gave in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I found this out later on when I read a book about her life and how brave she was and outspoken.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was never sentenced to death, because at that time the Russians were too close to Budapest to take over.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And everybody was really afraid that they are going to have to-- they be counted and asked about the crimes-- the war crimes-- they committed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So nobody wanted to do anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
